longBusinessSummary: AuSom Enterprise Limited operates as trading company in India. The company trades in commodities, bullions, gold jewelry, diamonds, derivatives, shares and securities, and units of mutual funds. AuSom Enterprise Limited was formerly known as Core Emballage Limited. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Ahmedabad, India.
